data.title: 'All My Children' Reveals L.A. Bound Cast List
data.meta_description: All My Children will not move west without its Daytime Emmy winning star, Susan Lucci . The actress will commute from east coast to west, deciding not to move her family from New York. The same goes for Vincent Irizarry (David). Today, the show released a list of cast members who would be making…
